WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Source: Articulate Closed Captions Editor
Source Version: 6.4.15731.0

00:00:00.256 --> 00:00:02.560
<b>Your wrist bends in four directions.</b>

00:00:02.816 --> 00:00:04.096
<b>Up toward your thumb.</b>

00:00:04.352 --> 00:00:05.888
<b>Down toward your little finger.</b>

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:07.424
<b>It flexes inward.</b>

00:00:07.936 --> 00:00:09.216
<b>And extends outward.</b>

00:00:09.728 --> 00:00:12.288
<b>Any of these four motions can be mid-range</b>

00:00:12.544 --> 00:00:13.832
<b>or end range.</b>

00:00:14.336 --> 00:00:18.688
<b>The end-range is the last few degrees of motion
before your wrist locks.</b>

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:20.480
<b>All the easy motion</b>

00:00:20.736 --> 00:00:22.584
<b>in the middle is mid-range.</b>

